data.description: Have you been eagerly scouring Zillow, Realtor, Redfin, and every nook and cranny of the internet’s real estate dynasty in search of your dream home? Allow me to usher you into this charming gem of a home. Welcome to this spacious single-family beauty, neatly tucked away in the coveted promised land of NLV! Let's gab about the layout. Imagine, a 1-story home with a 2-car garage, gracefully unfolding over 1502 square feet, this home is 2 beds, 2 baths, and a full den - easily could also be a bedroom. This spacious open floor plan has luxuriously upgraded carpets in the bedrooms and classy tiled in main areas. There's a backyard so immaculate you'll want to host summer BBQ’s year-round. The kitchen - so bright you'll need sunglasses! Gorgeous, upgraded granite countertops, an island large enough to host your own version of "Chopped," upgraded white cabinets, and equally sleek white appliances serve up a culinary paradise. So, folks, why are you still reading when you should be dialing?
